movie_name: The Making of Indiana Jones and the Dial of Destiny
short_description: Join the adventure with the cast and crew, showcasing new characters, stunts, music, locations, production design, and visual effects in five chapters that chart the making of Indiana Jones and the Dial of Destiny.
